The local Parquet file is Snappy-compressed, so I decoded the needed Parquet/Thrift/Snappy pieces directly in Node. The first exploratory pass shows strong PFS signals for metastatic burden, ECOG/stage, palbociclib, ER/PR, HER2, PIK3CA, albumin, age, weight loss, and inflammatory markers; I’m moving to adjusted models and treatment-by-biomarker interactions now.
